    "Dataset in medical and bioinformatics using DL approachesThe importance of datasets in DL applications in IoT-based bio-and medical informatics cannot be overstated.",
    "DL algorithms rely on large amounts of data to learn and make accurate predictions or classifications.",
    "In bio-and medical informatics, the availability of high-quality, comprehensive datasets is crucial for developing DL models that can accurately diagnose diseases, predict treatment outcomes, and identify potential drug targets.",
    "Furthermore, the success of DL models depends heavily on the quality and diversity of the data used to train them.",
    "A biased, incomplete, or unrepresentative dataset of the target population can lead to biased or inaccurate results [133]."
